  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bbe \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8- \u0b9a\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "India rushes to help as Sri Lanka suffers economic crisis - China does not respond to call for help - Samantha Power",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "USAID CEO Samantha Power says India has been quick to help Sri Lanka deal with the economic crisis but China has not responded to pleas for help.",
        "Samantha Power said that India responded quickly with very important measures to help Sri Lanka get out of the economic crisis.",
        "But the pleas of China for substantial relief have not been answered till the end, said Samantha Power.",
        "Samantha Power mentioned that China has become a major creditor country to Sri Lanka by providing non-transparent loans at higher interest rates than other lenders and questioned whether China will engage in debt restructuring to help Sri Lanka.",
        "He also said that India rushed into absolutely critical measures and pointed to the 3.5 billion dollar loan provided by India to Sri Lanka to help prevent Sri Lanka's bankruptcy and further decline.",
        "However, since 2000, China, which has given loans to Sri Lanka, has done the opposite to India, he said.",
        "China has become Sri Lanka's biggest lender over the past two decades by providing non-transparent high-interest loans and supporting infrastructure projects of dubious practicality, including a massive port that never generates even the tiniest returns, and a massive port that ships never use, says Samantha Power.",
        "He also said that India has helped the countries of the world in times of crisis.",
        "Samantha Power has said that China has promised to provide loans to Sri Lanka but has not provided them, Samantha Power has emphasized the need to adhere to democratic principles in her speech."
      ],
